source.name: Adoption and Child Custody Advocacy--2008 Home Investigation Data
source.description: The department is court ordered to complete a home investigation to determine if potential adoptive family whom is seeking permanency is suitable for placement. This data represents the number of home investigations undertaken by this office in 2008.
